description	"Rebel Smuggler

^2Weaponry:
- DL-44 Blaster Pistol (2)
- CR-1 Blast Cannon (2)
- 3 Detonation Packs

^8Attributes:
- Stamina (2)
- Reinforcements (1)
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^8[CS1]
- Slap ^3[CS2]
- Ammo Dispenser ^3[CS3]

The Rebel Smuggler is the engineer unit for the Rebel Alliance. His blast cannon shoots a wide spray of shots that will kill or cause great damage at close range. "